info.description:
pyspottedunipd

A tool to download, save, and analyze your Spotted Unipd posts data.

Install

- $ pip3 install . --upgrade --force-reinstall (install from source)

Questions and issues

The github issue tracker is only for bug reports and feature requests.    Anything else, such as questions for help in using the tool, should be posted as pull request
